                    "line_length": "4+8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Un lys mystérieux est tombé de sa main.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Les sanglots se sont tus brusquement… Elle passe…",
